Uses of Package
model

  • Packages that use model 
    Package Description
    mdxml  
    model  
  • Classes in model used by mdxml 
    Class and Description
    OwnedAttribute
    Represents attributes of classes which are described by PackagedElements
    OwnedOperation
    Represents an operation inside a PackagedElement
    PackagedElement
    Represents an element in the diagram.
    Xmi
    Class representing the root node of the xml file
  • Classes in model used by model 
    Class and Description
    Actual
    Auxiliary class representing the type replacing a Parameter in a ParameterSubstitution if the replacing type is a primitive type
    Client
    Represents the client class of an InterfaceRealization or Association.
    ConstrainingClassifier
    Describes a constraining classifier of an OwnedParameter in an OwnedTemplateSignature.
    DataType
    Represents a primitive data type which is described by a reference to its specification.
    DefaultValue
    Represents the default value of an OwnedAttribute
    DiagramContents
    Represents a list of ids of PackagedElements which are used in each diagram.
    DiagramRepresentation
    Describes the representation of a diagram by a DiagramRepresentationObject.
    DiagramRepresentationObject
    Object to represent a diagram and holds the DiagramContents of the diagram.
    Extension
    Represents an auxiliary node in the XML tree to extend the Magic Draw specification Used to hold a DiagramRepresentation, a ModelExtension or a ReferenceExtension
    Generalization
    Represents a generalization relationship of a PackagedElement and its general
    InterfaceRealization
    Represents a interface realization with the Supplier as the contract and the Client
    LowerValue
    Represents the lower value of an OwnedParameter or an OwnedAttribute
    MemberEnd
    References the end of an association with the id of the corresponding PackagedElement
    Model
    Represents a model in the given Magic Draw project
    ModelExtension
    Represents an auxiliary node in the XML tree held by an Extension Holds LowerValues and UpperValues when used by an OwnedAttribute or OwnedDiagrams when used by the Model
    OwnedAttribute
    Represents attributes of classes which are described by PackagedElements
    OwnedDiagram
    Describes a diagram which is further specified by a DiagramRepresentation, DiagramRepresentationObject and DiagramContents which are held by an Extension
    OwnedEnd
    Describes the owned end of an association
    OwnedLiteral
    Represents enumeration literals held by a PackagedElement representing the enumeration
    OwnedOperation
    Represents an operation inside a PackagedElement
    OwnedParameter
    Represents parameters of OwnedOperations and OwnedTemplateSignatures
    OwnedParameteredElement
    Describes an element which is parametered by an OwnedParameter
    OwnedTemplateSignature
    Represents a template signature of a PackagedElement which represents a class or an interface
    PackagedElement
    Represents an element in the diagram.
    Parameter
    Represents a reference to an OwnedParameter in an OwnedTemplateSignature
    ParameterSubstitution
    Represents a substitution of a template Parameter
    ReferenceExtension
    Determines the data type of a primitive type by holding a reference to its specification
    Supplier
    Represents the supplier class of an InterfaceRealization or Association.
    TemplateBinding
    Represents a template binding by an OwnedOperation or PackagedElement
    UpperValue
    Represents the upper value of an OwnedParameter or an OwnedAttribute
